    ["Ny'alotha: MOTHER's Guidance"] = "Ny'alotha: La guía de MADRE",
    ["Oblivion stacks don't matter anymore, but avoid swirly/portal-looking areas on the ground. Stay away from the edge."] = "Las acumulaciones de Oblivion ya no importan, pero evita las zonas arremolinadas con aspecto de portal que aparecen en el suelo. Aléjate del borde.",
    ["Odious Gwor"] = "Gwor, el Odioso",
    ["On the beach, your goal is to destroy (7) ^Kor'kron Cannons^. Click the ^Spike Mines^ next to each cannon to destroy them."] = "En la playa, debes destruir (7) ^Kor'kron Cannons^. Pulsa las ^Spike Mines^ que hay junto a cada cañón para destruirlos.",
    ["On the other side of the gate, proceed ahead to engage ^Iron Qon^."] = "Al otro lado de la puerta, avanza para enfrentarte a ^Iron Qon^.",
    ["Once in the ^Ring of Containment^, head to the leftmost map exit labeled ^Archives of Eternity^."] = "Al llegar a ^Ring of Containment^, dirígete a la salida del extremo izquierdo llamada ^Archives of Eternity^.",
    ["Once inside ^Artifact Storage^, continue forward and click on the ^Secured Stockpile of Pandaren Spoils^ to begin the ^Spoils of Pandaria^ encounter."] = "Dentro de ^Artifact Storage^, avanza y pulsa el ^Secured Stockpile of Pandaren Spoils^ para iniciar el encuentro de ^Spoils of Pandaria^.",
    ["Once inside ^Loa's Sanctum^, follow the path straight ahead to engage ^Conclave of the Chosen^."] = "Dentro de ^Loa's Sanctum^, sigue el camino de frente para enfrentarte a ^Conclave of the Chosen^.",
    ["Once inside ^Moonglade^, work your way down to ^Cenarius^ and kill him."] = "Dentro de ^Moonglade^, baja hasta ^Cenarius^ y mátalo.",
    ["Once inside ^Mulgore^, follow the path around, and clear the trash on your way to ^Elerethe Renferal^."] = "Dentro de ^Mulgore^, sigue el camino y elimina a los enemigos de camino a ^Elerethe Renferal^.",
    ["Once the door opens, proceed through it and climb some stairs to reach ^Star Augur Etraeus^."] = "Cuando se abra la puerta, crúzala y sube las escaleras hasta ^Star Augur Etraeus^.",
    ["Once you arrive in ^Feast of Arrogance^, follow the path to find ^The Council of Blood^ at the far end of the room."] = "Al llegar a ^Feast of Arrogance^, sigue el camino hasta ^The Council of Blood^, al fondo de la sala.",
    ["Once you arrive in the ^Eye of Eternity^, click ^The Focusing Iris^ to start the encounter with ^Hagara the Stormbinder^."] = "Al llegar a ^Eye of Eternity^, pulsa ^The Focusing Iris^ para iniciar el encuentro con ^Hagara the Stormbinder^.",
    ["Once you enter the ^Elarian Sanctuary^, approach the ^Essence of Eonar^ (blue floating orb), and interact with it to begin the encounter for ^Eonar the Life-Binder^."] = "Al entrar en ^Elarian Sanctuary^, acércate a ^Essence of Eonar^, el orbe azul flotante, e interactúa con él para iniciar el encuentro de ^Eonar the Life-Binder^.",
    ["Once you land, take the middle (and final) path labeled ^The Clutchwarren^."] = "Al aterrizar, toma el camino central, el último disponible, llamado ^The Clutchwarren^.",
    ["Once you reach ^Helheim^, follow the path around to find ^Guarm^."] = "Al llegar a ^Helheim^, sigue el camino hasta ^Guarm^.",
    ["Once you reach ^Shal'dorei Terrace^, make your way over to ^High Botanist Tel'arn^ to begin the encounter."] = "Al llegar a ^Shal'dorei Terrace^, dirígete a ^High Botanist Tel'arn^ para iniciar el encuentro.",
    ["Once you reach the ^Ring of Containment^, take a right and head for the map exit labeled ^Gallery of Failures^."] = "Al llegar a ^Ring of Containment^, gira a la derecha y dirígete a la salida del mapa llamada ^Gallery of Failures^.",
    ["Once you reach the bottom of the elevator, take the southern path to reach ^Hans'gar and Franzok^. After a brief dialog, kill the trash to start the encounter."] = "Al llegar al fondo del ascensor, toma el camino sur hasta ^Hans'gar and Franzok^. Después del breve diálogo, mata a los enemigos para iniciar el encuentro.",
    ["Once you reach the top of the elevator, follow the path to the north to reach ^The Crucible^."] = "Al llegar arriba del ascensor, sigue el camino hacia el norte hasta ^The Crucible^.",
    ["Once you're in mid-flight, talk to ^Sky Captain Swayze^ again to begin the encounter with ^Warmaster Blackhorn^."] = "Durante el vuelo, vuelve a hablar con ^Sky Captain Swayze^ para iniciar el encuentro con ^Warmaster Blackhorn^.",
